author: @enairap2175
text:
[Verse 1]
At some point, unknowingly
My steps that had strayed
Became unable to turn back
When they had gone too far away
Perhaps it's too late
Or could it be too fast
Where have I come to?
When I'm tired of anxiety

[Pre-Chorus]
Close your eyes and listen
To the melody the wind carries to you
You'll come to know, when that time comes, it'll dazzle you
When that time comes, It'll brightly illuminate you

[Chorus]
It's okay to stumble for a moment
Because it will soon start again
Even if you take a break for a moment on this path just for you
It was just a rest comma to make you shine again

[Post-Chorus]
Just a rest comma
No, woah, no, woah

[Verse 2]
The long times we ran out of breath
They all have significant meaning

[Pre-Chorus]
When our eyes meet and we tilt our heads
One by one, we hear harmony
You'll come to know, when that time comes, it'll dazzle you
When that time comes, it'll brightly illuminate you, woah, woah

[Chorus]
It's okay to stumble for a moment
Because it will soon start again
Even if you take a break for a moment on this path just for you
It was just a rest comma to make you shine again

[Bridge]
There's no predetermined path according to your heart
Let go of past worries
And become harmony in all your moments
We'll paint the same tomorrow together

[Chorus]
It's okay even if it comes to an end
Because it will be a new beginning
Even if you take a break for a moment
A new song will gradually be written, ooh

[Outro]
Na-na-na, na-na-na
Na-na-na, na-na, na-na
Na-na-na, na-na-na
It was just a rest comma
Na-na-na, na-na-na (Oh, oh, oh)
Na-na-na, na-na, na-na
Na-na-na, na-na-na (Oh, woah)
It was just a rest comma

text: Doyoung, I've been your fan since I was in 2nd grade of elementary school, I first got to know you because of exo. Now I will graduate from junior high schoolðŸ˜¿ Doyoung, I want to say one thing, Doyoung, I sometimes feel like I want to stop being your fan. I'm so tired, I want to be an ordinary person. I finally decided to take a break and not participate in all your activities, but that only lasted for 3 weeks, it turns out I couldn't leave you, it turns out you are the source of my happiness that I can't leave, you are God's destiny to be the source of my happiness. Doyoung, remain an idol that I can trust. Doyoung, I sometimes cry when I hear your song entitled "rest". It turns out there's nothing wrong if I want to rest for a while. Doyoung, thank you for singing that song, I feel motivated. Now I will continue to follow all your activities, I will support you even though not completely. Doyoung I just hope you make your words come true "we will not be reduced" I hope it can come true and I hope you read my message. In essence, thank you for staying together, I'm sorry that I left you for three weeks. I love you guys, especially doyoung (Forgive me for making this sentence, because I use Google Translate)
